thread.title: Dean Kenyon
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Dean Kenyon

author: Dean Kenyon
title: Dean Kenyon
text: We were very happy with our rental. Airport pickup was fast and staff were very pleasant and helpful. We were repeat customers and were offered a better local rate which was great. The Nissan we rented functioned very well. On return, no sooner had we driven into the depo and we were wisked back to the airport within minutes. Highly recommend!
